Package Responses

Class LoginResponse

java.lang.Object
Responses.FMSResponse
Responses.LoginResponse
public class LoginResponse
extends FMSResponse
The result of a request to the /user/login or /user/register endpoint. The outcome of an attempt to log a user into or register a new user with the server.
